A vintage-style illustration of an open hardcover book resting on a wooden desk, its pages transforming into delicate origami cranes that flutter upward and scatter across the scene. Cherry blossom petals drift through warm golden afternoon light streaming through a nearby window with rice paper panels. A steaming cup of green tea sits beside the book. The color palette features warm sepia tones, soft pinks, and muted greens, reminiscent of 1960s Japanese travel posters with subtle texture and grain throughout the image.
